Imagine:

All EC2s share the same network
No private IPs
No subnet isolation
No custom routing
No VPN or Direct Connect

ğŸš¨ Massive security and scalability nightmare

VPC solves this by giving per-customer network ownership.

4ï¸âƒ£ Real-World Analogy (Easy to Remember)
AWS Concept	Real-World Analogy
Region	City
VPC	Private building
