Part	Meaning
10.0.0.0	Network address
/16	First 16 bits are network bits
Remaining bits	Host addresses
IPv4 has 32 bits total:

16 bits (network) + 16 bits (hosts)
3ï¸âƒ£ How many IPs in a CIDR block?
Formula:

2^(32 - prefix)
CIDR	Total IPs
/8	16,777,216
/16	65,536
/24	256
/28	16
